<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[الغُسالة]</span>: ما سقط عن الغَسْل.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>... فَعُول<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
